{"tid":1579450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星期六唔好去沙田","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T07:00:51.000Z","uid":281492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a98ccec76dd00824049986cc2a575c944484f90c","tid":1579450,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"要留返命仔做文宣同其他活動<br />\n<br />\n同班警黑鬥侖長<br />\n<br />\n等佢哋到時無嘢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af0cd79dd09d332682e61df1540b5c2ccda1bcd","tid":1579450,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqctagq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnqctagq.png&h=7fed4eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友係福建人<br />\n<br />\n佢話何生琴日係街比馬迷鬧係過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n新聞訪問阿叔又係咁鬧何生<br />\n<br />\n何生依家準備吹大雞要打馬迷 開始召集福建幫<br />\n<br />\n仲話呢排一見到有人拎馬經就話要打<br />\n<br />\n佢地今次唔係針對果班暴徒曱甴<br />\n<br />\n係針對我地班馬迷 各位黎緊跑馬既馬迷要小心！<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安"}]}